      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical code must be verified against analytical solutions or method-of-manufactured solutions for all relevant flow regimes at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed for simple pipe flow but not for the rotating impeller geometry or non-Newtonian blood rheology relevant to VAD hemolysis prediction. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for MRL 5."
