      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel or U95 band) between predicted and measured hemolysis index must be reported with uncertainty bounds at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Output comparison was performed qualitatively with trend agreement noted but no quantitative error metric or uncertainty band reported. Achieved level 2 does not satisfy the MRL 5 requirement of level 4."
