      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoI (normalized index of hemolysis, NIH) must be directly traceable to the clinical hemolysis threshold specified in the COU at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The model outputs modified index of hemolysis (MIH) which requires an empirical conversion factor to obtain NIH. The conversion introduces additional uncertainty not propagated through the Monte Carlo analysis. Achieved level 2 is below required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
