      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis damage model form (power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger or equivalent) must be justified against alternative model forms with sensitivity analysis at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty was not assessed. Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law was applied without comparison to alternative hemolysis models. Flagged as epistemic gap; achieved level 1 reflects no model-form evidence."
    },
